OL,3,CPope Leo XIV carries cross for full
OL,4,CGood Friday procession
OL,6,FPope Leo XIV has become the first
OL,7,Fpontiff in decades to carry a wooden
OL,8,Fcross for the 14 stations of the Way
OL,9,Fof the Cross on his first Good Friday
OL,10,Fas Holy Father.
OL,12,FInside the Colosseum, Leo began the
OL,13,Fprocession flanked by two young people
OL,14,Fholding torches, and followed by
OL,15,Fclergy.
OL,17,FThousands gathered outside the
OL,18,Fmonument in Rome, where the procession
OL,19,Fcontinued, following the stations as
OL,20,Fthey were recited over loud speakers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
