OL,3,CPope Leo XIV carries cross for full
OL,4,CGood Friday procession
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThey included Sister Pelenatita Kieoma
OL,12,FFinau from Samoa and a member of the
OL,13,FMissionary Sisters of the Society of
OL,14,FMary.
OL,16,FShe said: "We have been part of our
OL,17,Fparish stations of the cross, but this
OL,18,Fis so exciting. It is very meaningful
OL,19,Fto have the experience of being with
OL,20,Fthe people of Rome on this special
OL,21,Foccasion."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
