PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775311858
OL,3,CPope Leo XIV carries cross for full
OL,4,CGood Friday procession
OL,6,FIn previous years, John Paul II
OL,7,Fcarried the cross for the entire
OL,8,Fprocession from his first Good Friday
OL,9,Fas pontiff in 1979 until his hip
OL,10,Fsurgery in 1995, when he carried it
OL,11,Fjust part of the way.
OL,13,FFor the first two years of his papacy,
OL,14,FBenedict XVI carried the cross for the
OL,15,Ffirst station inside the Colosseum,
OL,16,Fthen followed other bearers in the
OL,17,Fprocession that ends on a platform on
OL,18,Fthe Palatine Hill.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
