SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775311858
OL,3,CPope Leo XIV carries cross for full
OL,4,CGood Friday procession
OL,6,FPope Francis never carried the cross,
OL,7,Fbut participated in the procession
OL,8,Funtil his health worsened. He died
OL,9,Fafter a long illness last year on
OL,10,FEaster Monday, which fell on April 21.
OL,12,FThe Way of the Cross commemorates the
OL,13,Ffinal hours of Jesus' life, from his
OL,14,Fdeath sentence to taking up the cross
OL,15,Fto his crucifixion, death and burial.
OL,16,FThe procession ends outside the
OL,17,FColosseum atop the Palatine Hill.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
