OL,3,CPope Leo XIV carries cross for full
OL,4,CGood Friday procession
OL,6,FOn Holy Saturday, the pontiff will
OL,7,Fpreside over a late night Easter
OL,8,Fvigil, during which he will baptise
OL,9,Fnew Catholics, and lead Roman
OL,10,FCatholics into Christianity's most
OL,11,Fjoyous celebration marking Christ's
OL,12,Fresurrection.
OL,14,FOn Easter Sunday, the pope will
OL,15,Fcelebrate an open-air Mass in St.
OL,16,FPeter's Square before delivering his
OL,17,FEaster message and offer the
OL,18,Ftraditional "Urbi et Orbi" blessing to
OL,19,Fthe city of Rome and the world.
